<MainLayout title="Baseball & Softball Banquet Planning Guide" description="Complete guide to planning a high school baseball or softball banquet. Senior night traditions, team awards, decorations, and custom baseball/softball centerpiece recommendations.">
  <div class="breadcrumbs">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="/banquet-planning/">Banquet Guide</a> <span>/</span> <strong>Baseball & Softball Banquet</strong>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Baseball & Softball Banquet Planning Guide</h1>
      <p>Diamond sports have deep traditions. From the first pitch to the final out, your banquet should honor the season's journey.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-wrapper">
        <h2>Baseball & Softball Planning</h2>
        <p>These programs often have JV and varsity levels and may overlap with spring sports seasons. Coordinate early with athletic directors to find dates that don't conflict with other spring sports banquets.</p>

        <h3>Baseball Decor Themes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Dugout Dinner</strong> — Rustic baseball-themed decor with bats, gloves, and dirt-colored linens</li>
          <li><strong>Field of Dreams</strong> — Classic, nostalgic theme focused on tradition</li>
          <li><strong>Home Run Celebration</strong> — Stats-focused theme highlighting team and individual achievements</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Softball Decor Themes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Diamond Divas</strong> — Glam meets athletic with team colors and soft lighting</li>
          <li><strong>Strike Out the Night</strong> — Bold colors and action photography</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Baseball & Softball Awards</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Team MVP</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Batting Champion</strong> — Highest average</li>
          <li><strong>Cy Young Award</strong> — Best pitcher (ERA/Wins)</li>
          <li><strong>Gold Glove</strong> — Defensive excellence</li>
          <li><strong>Silver Slugger</strong> — Top offensive performer</li>
          <li><strong>Most Improved</strong></li>
          <li><strong>Coach's Award</strong></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="product-note">
          <h3>⚾ Custom Baseball & Softball Centerpieces</h3>
          <p>Personalized baseball or softball centerpieces for banquet tables. Each piece is handcrafted with detailed stitching and seam lines, available in team colors with optional name/number personalization. Great for banquet tables and senior night gifts.</p>
          <p><a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/collections/all" target="_blank" class="card-link">Shop Baseball & Softball Centerpieces →</a></p>
        </div>

        <p><a href="/banquet-planning/" class="btn btn-outline">Full Banquet Guide →</a> <a href="/award-ceremony/" class="btn btn-outline">Award Ceremony Tips →</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

